Build a Charleston Area Home Search & Analysis Web Application

Objective

Build a professional real estate analysis application that automatically searches, aggregates, analyzes, ranks, and presents homes for sale in the Charleston, South Carolina metro area that meet the criteria below.

The application should function similarly to a premium real estate analytics platform rather than simply displaying listings.

The intended user is relocating from Greenville, SC to the Charleston area and wants objective financial and lifestyle analysis to make the best purchasing decision.

